file=Cybersecurity/warden/custom/third-party-risk/README.md · s—m:SUPERSEDED — moved to marketplace/=This custom skill has been replaced by the verbatim marketplace adoption of **Anthropic vendor-review** at `marketplace/third-party-risk/SKILL.md`.\n\n**Reason for superseding (per CYBERSECURITY-REDESIGN-PLAN-v2 §1.3):** The Anthropic official vendor-review skill covers the full assessment cycle (TCO, risk, performance, comparison) better than the custom version. It's official Anthropic IP, maintained, and portable. Supplemented by `marketplace/vendor-ai-risk/SKILL.md` for AI-specific vendor assessments.\n\n**Superseded on:** 2026-07-12\n\nThe custom vendor-assessment-template.md asset is retained as a supplementary file if needed.\n